data.description: Welcome to 261 W Idaho Ave Irrigon OR. This home contains four bedrooms, two bathrooms and a large open living space. This allows for ease of entertaining guests and cooking on the stainless steel appliances. If you prefer to be outside this home has 2.0 Acres of land with 1.7 Acres of WATER RIGHTS. The large outdoor patio is great for enjoying the evenings, watching the sunset and lighting the bbq all summer long. The hickory shed and solid set sprinklers allow the ease of having animals and more. Plenty of room for all of your hobbies indoor and outdoor! Call TODAY to set up your private showing.
